{"tid":1466273,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母又話核彈都唔割 而家做乜撚嘢啊","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:38:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:57:26.000Z","uid":2174,"like":26,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1118af2725f567f578de6011e5716701c86e2045","tid":1466273,"uid":2174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:38:42.000Z","msg":"冷氣軍師 香港真係多得你呢啲人<br />\n手足救人警察舉真槍 你係到屌啲前線？<br />\n你係屋企打緊飛機咋<br />\n你睇下而家機場啲黑警畜龍樣都唔比你睇啊<br />\n你係屋企mon緊post咋 屌你老母<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不割蓆</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">支持前線</span></span>"},{"pid":"8b02f6587aa9f608a7d7f1e4c9f735a862b7dced","tid":1466273,"uid":2174,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:39:25.000Z","msg":"好撚嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f362222b53bf7b3746874dba392fe6e67ce91227","tid":1466273,"uid":52574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:39:37.000Z","msg":"從來都唔係【癱唔癱】既問題，而係【如何癱】既問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464999\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464999</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n求大家睇下同投個票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今晚係轉捩點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c18f4ccfb643c85ba656f5f1025c44e5016af13","tid":1466273,"uid":224779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:39:53.000Z","msg":"唔完美 可接受"},{"pid":"09dcaa9e0e3552a67a3b3d85f696f037bf7e73d5","tid":1466273,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:40:02.000Z","msg":"做錯就要認<br />\nbe humble 唔係盲撐"},{"pid":"f3a83d2727ae19758f59d27c7f79e27f12b52d83","tid":1466273,"uid":41875,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:40:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">失敗主義</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">解散軍</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">大台</span>出沒注意</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">連登忽然出現大量打手</span><br />\n<br />\n行動有鬼<br />\n=&gt;鬼嘅特徵<br />\n=&gt;掛住捉鬼<br />\n=&gt;互相猜忌<br />\n=&gt;限制行動<br />\n=&gt;出現糾察<br />\n=&gt;話人搞事<br />\n=&gt;分化大眾<br />\n=&gt;大台形成<br />\n<br />\n大家要留意呢排有好多人包括現場人士，議員，KOL限制你地嘅行動，講出似是而非，要保護邊個邊個唔好咁做，呢啲行為完全推翻呢2個月be water，兄弟爬山，不分化不割蓆嘅行動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">小心解散軍。義士們，我相信你地！</span>"},{"pid":"17e408f0d1183ee447c5db0a2ed62d63f060d038","tid":1466273,"uid":140431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:40:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f57aa1f75f452374cc0bee9646747d960ff81a30","tid":1466273,"uid":38204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:40:13.000Z","msg":"無 收order要開工啫"},{"pid":"13749481c1524f6abe8f52f99f96093748df4bd1","tid":1466273,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:40:31.000Z","msg":"唔完美，可接受，但需要改善，改進，不割席"},{"pid":"5950d44a4497af060bf374e72954ba43ef0b612d","tid":1466273,"uid":54051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:40:36.000Z","msg":"冇佢地 又少一個前線 做得好！！"},{"pid":"b14472bf1304d69c74b49df0c37e9455de79532a","tid":1466273,"uid":124452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:40:40.000Z","msg":"咪撚分化啦你<br />\n<br />\n你咁做咪又係割和理非<br />\n<br />\n重申係要互相尊重 互相唔割"},{"pid":"0fedc6dab919882650c67329f78a9816a3c34251","tid":1466273,"uid":2174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:40:50.000Z","msg":"你夠膽就而家係屋企死出嚟機場 睇下你仲割唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"984342dc82cf61be478451706e2af8f6c0f0418a","tid":1466273,"uid":299202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:40:55.000Z","msg":"I have nothing to say"},{"pid":"136e969b7e119546c118cf53f11cb9c85b635347","tid":1466